high_descs: Turn right and move to the counter near the window.
Pick up the knife with the gold handle from the counter.
Move around the counter to the right of the black stool in front of the window .
Slice the apple in the center of the counter using the knife.
Turn to the right, move towards the blue trash bin, then turn to the left, move towards the brown coffee maker, then turn to the right and move to the red microwave.
Open the microwave door and place the knife in front of the egg on the plate then close the microwave door.
Turn right, move toward the range, then turn right and move toward the window, then turn right and move to the black stool, then turn and face the counter.
Take one apple slice from the sliced apple.
Turn to the right, move towards the blue trash bin, then turn to the left, move towards the brown coffee maker, then turn to the right and move to the red microwave.
Open the microwave, place the apple slice on the plate to the left of the egg, microwave the slice, open the microwave door, take the apple slice from the plate, then close the microwave door.
Turn right, move towards the range, then turn left and face the sink.
Place the apple slice in the front of the sink between the fork and the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked apple slice in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go straight to the counter.
Take the knife from the counter.
Go to the other side of the counter, facing towards the microwave.
Cut the apple on the counter into pieces.
Go around the counter to the right, then go straight to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around, go back across the room to the other side of the counter facing the microwave.
Take a piece of apple from the counter.
Go around the counter to the right, then go straight to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave, take the apple from the microwave.
Turn right, go to the sink.
Put the apple in the sink between the fork and the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the counter.
Pick up the yellow knife from the counter.
Take a step to the left.
Slice the apple on the counter in three pieces.
Turn right, walk past the counter, and then turn left towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the knife in it, and close the microwave.
Turn back around towards the counter.
Pick up a slice of apple from the counter.
Turn around and head towards the microwave.
Open the microwave, place the apple in it, heat it up, and pick the apple back out.
Turn right and head towards the sink on your left.
Place the apple slice in between the spatula and fork in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a warm slice of apple in the sink.
